<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="joy-n">joy <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dʒɔɪ/    美 /dʒɔɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>欢乐；高兴：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>jumped for joy</strong> when I heard the good news. 
听到这个好消息我高兴得跳了起来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>To our joy</strong> we found him alive. 
令我们欣喜的是，他还活着。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>乐事；乐趣：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>our joys and sadnesses
我们的欢乐与悲伤</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Listening to music is one of my greatest joys. 
听音乐是我的一大乐事。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>joyful /'dʒɔɪfl/ adj <br />
joyous /ˈdʒɔɪəs/ adj   </p></div>